channel.title: Problem with jarring the client
channel.description:
Hey, i have a PI Client. I'm trying to jar it, but always when i create the jar, it doesn't open up. Before every client got jarred perfectly and worked, but this doesn't? Maybe because my .class files are not located after /bin/ ? Because if i go on /bin/ there is another directory called /com/, and in this directory are the class files located. (Some class files are located in a few directorys too, example: /bin/com/blabla/meow.class
Anyone?
